<br>
1) Your uber mobs are Kunark raid mobs, in which case you're correct, with the exception of Gorenaire, we can't really hit anything.<br>
2) You're fighting Velious/Luclin &quot;uber&quot; mobs, but are too low level.<br>
<br>
Tunare is the only uber mob outside of Kunark that I can't land nukes on with the same resist rates as normal exp mobs.  Getting a lure spell would be nice for those mobs in Kunark, but wouldn't be of benefit else where.  Our wizards almost never use lures anymore because they're so inefficient. <p>~~
